 </div>
 
 <div>
  <a class="image" href="https://forums.kicksecure.com" target="_blank" style="background-image:url('/w/images/a/af/Discourse_logo.png');" title="Forums and more"></a>
  <h4>Vibrant Community</h4>
  <p>
   Our vibrant Kicksecure community features
   <a class="read-more" href="https://forums.kicksecure.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Forums</a> and
